Class WauzLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.wauz.wauzcore.WauzLoader

  • public class WauzLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Used by the main class to load all static data. Contains different private methods for all data types (commands, equip etc.).

      • init

        public static void init()
        Calls all other methods for loading and initializing data. Also cleans data from last run by recalculating the statistics and removing inactive instances. Only called once per server run.
        See Also:
        InstanceManager.removeInactiveInstances(), StatisticsFetcher.calculate()
